    <!--About activity-->
    <string name="about_about_app_title">About this app</string>
    <string name="about_about_app_large_text">
        "Dash notes, a simple notes app aims to use stock android features.\n\n"

        "Dash notes utilizes stock android quick settings tiles and notification services to provide fast, easy note-taking experience to users. It also gives you a fresh look in UI. Some material design 2 styles have been implemented, such as snackbar and the bottom sheet view.\n\n"

        "Dash notes comes very handy when you need to jot some notes, such as:\n"
        " - creating a buying list\n"
        " - making some reminders for yourself\n"
        " - jotting down some important messages\n"
        " - writing some mottos\n"
        "and much more! Explore your own ways to use this app!\n\n"

        "Keep in mind that this app may not support android with skins, such as MIUI, EMUI, Flyme, Funtouch OS…And they will never be supported unless the system developer add back the BASIC Android features.\n\n"

        "If you face any question or want to give suggestions about anything, feel free to contact me:P"
    </string>

